    <string name="about_specura">About SPECURA</string>
    <string name="about_specura_body">SPECURA is a lightweight AI-assisted mobile application designed for construction material recognition, visible damage assessment, and condition monitoring. The system uses MobileCLIP-based image inference together with OpenCV image processing to analyze material surfaces such as concrete, brick, metal, and wood.\n\nThe application can identify visible surface irregularities, estimate severity levels, and maintain scan history records for monitoring changes over time. SPECURA is intended as a decision-support and educational tool for preliminary material inspection and assessment.</string>
